    "text": "Lily’s Petting Farm, Gaborone \nThis is not just a petting farm. But a place to spend the entire day with your children. \nYou have a jungle gym, swings, a slide. And a pool that is not too deep.  \nSome nice farm animals too. For the children to stroke and feed. \nSadly the lady at the entrance is rather grim. No welcome from her. \nBut after that, the staff around are cheerful and helpful. \nDo take your food and drinks along, relax. Enjoy the place. They do have a small canteen.",
